metadata.name: SOUTH PEPE APRIL FOOLS EDITION
metadata.description:
You can just hang outside in the sun all day tossing a ball around. Or you can sit at your computer and do something that matters... 

Let's get Rekt on the way to 69 ETH. 

Re-imagining one of the greatest troll episodes in adult cartoons.
